{"tid":1103852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張超雄 真係多謝曬你","createTime":"2019-04-12T16:23:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T17:17:32.000Z","uid":143372,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"78b99a28be1f515d221025ddab6c4eae6cd95ce3","tid":1103852,"uid":143372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T16:23:53.000Z","msg":"猅仔插人面 蝻狗玩鎗擊<br />\n一星期兩單 張超雄你最爽啦<br />\n<br />\n呢啲低等人種一早就知係危險人啦<br />\n佢地凶殘個種基因係深殖係佢地細胞到<br />\n你試下行落深水涉啲蝻望住啲後生女個樣係好似隨時準備好交配咁 好撚似睇緊異型<br />\n呢家成香港都係呢啲危險動物 <br />\n係要放佢地入香港嘅<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你有報應㗎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19a5a888a2d2961c30eb37415473121e91b57a42","tid":1103852,"uid":126309,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T16:40:39.000Z","msg":"係難民之父就應該搬入埋深水埗照顧佢地"},{"pid":"8f6f5f31cf6553f1510b0fbe4c0988ead21cdd9f","tid":1103852,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T16:48:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係夠哂nice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a73cce2b71555a4eab5681c7a42a7e1838b5c7e","tid":1103852,"uid":44391,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T16:56:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd673eb10f3d6ed2cf99f29b91caa6d9e09c9532","tid":1103852,"uid":5378,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T16:57:13.000Z","msg":"為左票 為左議席 為左錢 乜鳩都做得出架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d4963e30f643e820949009a8266d3f5941d5a0","tid":1103852,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19a5a888a2d2961c30eb37415473121e91b57a42","tid":1103852,"uid":126309,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"rep